long.am,ar,bg,bn,el,et,fa,fil,gu,he,hi,hr,hu,:
This is NOT a YouTube Downloader. Unfortunately, due to restrictions of the Google Web Store Policies and Developer Program Policies, we cannot download YouTube videos. Thank you for understanding.

Our Video Downloader will help you find and quickly download any video and music from 98% of web pages all over the Internet. 

Click on the extension icon and see all files available for download. Choose a file and give it a second to be saved on your computer. It is the best video downloader Chrome extension, allowing you to download video or audio in Chrome quickly and easily.

-----------------------------------------------

Why do you need it?

- Any available format can be downloaded.
- No need to waste time searching for available video — this extension will do it for you.
- No ads, spyware, or malware.
- Easy to uninstall.
- No need to register an account to use it. You can download any video or audio without registering. This extension is free to use.

-----------------------------------------------

The video downloader is a useful Chrome extension to download every video from each website you want. With this extension, you can download videos from thousands of websites in different qualities and lengths and save them to your disk.

You can preview the video before downloading it. You can see the video size and format before downloading. You can choose the quality on the downloading page before downloading.

-----------------------------------------------

Ultimate Video Downloader

- Download videos playing on a website to a hard disk
- Play videos before you download them
- Select between different resolutions if the site supports it

-----------------------------------------------

Please note: 

Some web pages require you to start playing the video first to help Video Downloader find it.

Due to the privacy policies and terms of use of Google and YouTube, videos cannot be downloaded from YouTube. However, you can use the video downloader to download and save any video you want on many other websites.
long.ca:

Ultimate Video Downloader

Některé webové stránky vyžadují, abyste nejprve spustili přehrávání videa, aby je Video Downloader pomohl najít.
